wn.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T05:30:54.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhP2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=82de3367\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！"},{"pid":"2d488499ae7ba6d0dd7dd991cb96d55e87d262d7","tid":1168152,"uid":59090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"435e1ab3604225343be6eec19419940eab2ce7f6","tid":1168152,"uid":212500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:13:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T05:40:15.000Z","msg":"呢個世界本來就唔會有人完全明白第二個人"},{"pid":"c56703ed260e94b08d7eee77e8ea8b73b540064c","tid":1168152,"uid":212500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d488499ae7ba6d0dd7dd991cb96d55e87d262d7","tid":1168152,"uid":59090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"435e1ab3604225343be6eec19419940eab2ce7f6","tid":1168152,"uid":212500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:13:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,